        I blabber about my unsolicited opinions in Hebrew.
    </p>
    <h3>Links</h3>
    <p class="links">
        <a href="https://www.github.com/r0nsha" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ron-shavit-b3b7074b/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://www.ptsg.dev" target="_blank">Podcast</a>
